title: WTF CNN, Receipts?! 1.16.19

description:
In episode 550, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Harper-Rose Drummond to discuss a new water obstacle competition show, the Democratic debates, impeachment updates, a racist YouTuber asking for money, Bill O'Reilly 'not doing well,' a chef asking people to stop taking photos of their food, the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Mike “The Miz” Mizanin To Cohost USA Network’s Water Challenge Competition ‘Cannonball’
  2. CNN: “You’re saying that you never told Senator Warren that a woman couldn’t win the election?”
  3. Docs Reveal Trump and Giuliani‘s ‘Personal Henchmen‘ Were ‘Physically Stalking a U.S. Ambassador’
  4. New Lev Parnas Documents Suggest U.S. Ambassador Was Under Surveillance In Ukraine
  5. Did Trump Goons Stalk Ambassador Marie Yovanovitch?
  6. Man Who Claimed Lipstick Was Like A Boner On Your Face Can't Get Job
  7. Instagram food porn: Top U.K. chef reignites debate over diners’ meal pics
  8. Whitney Houston, Nine Inch Nails, and Biggie Lead 2020 Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Induction Class
  9. WATCH: Bastien Keb - Pork Belly
